Radio presenter Mwende Macharia is expecting her second child. Announcing the good news on Instagram, the mother of one shared photos from her recent baby bump shoot. "Behold, I do a new thing. Joy unspeakable. After seven years, I am mum again," she captioned it. Adding, "Queen Mother. All the glory be to God." She, however, has not revealed her baby daddy. Mwende sired her firstborn son with music producer J blessing. According to the bubbly radio presenter, she was engaged to J Blessing and the wedding plans were in the pipeline as he had even met her parents in Diani. She told Parent's magazine that J Blessing was already not committed to their relationship by the time she discovered she was pregnant for him. He is rumoured to be the father of Avril's baby.